---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about YardFavorites - who we are, our mission, and why we test products the way we do."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-purple-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About YardFavorites</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200">Real homeowners. Real tests. Honest reviews.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose prose-lg">
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>
        YardFavorites started because we were tired of reviews that felt like advertisements.
        As homeowners ourselves, we bought every product at full retail price and used them
        in real conditions — not just unboxed and photographed.
      </p>
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        We're a small team of homeowners, DIY enthusiasts, and outdoor living fans based
        in the United States. We test products across real pools, patios, and yards
        throughout the seasons.
      </p>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        To help homeowners make confident purchasing decisions with honest, detailed,
        and practical product information — whether that product comes from Amazon,
        a big-box store, or a direct manufacturer.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question or want to suggest a product for us to test?
        Reach out at <strong>hello@yardfavorites.com</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
